Taylor Pickett bụ otu n'ime ndị na-ese ihe nkè e gosipụtara ọrụ ya na 1986 otu ngosi Progressions: Cultural Legacy na MoMA PS1.
Kamala Harris bụ ónyé na-akwado ọrụ Taylor Pickett. E gosipụtara otu n'ime ihe osise nke onye na-ese ihe n'ọfịs ndị omeiwu mgbè Harris bụ ónyé omeiwu.
